milestones.description: Zaheer Abbas has scored 9 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for PAK breaking Majid Khan's record
Zaheer Abbas has broken the record for most sixes (10) in ODIs for PAK, going past Wasim Raja's 9
Zaheer Abbas and Javed Miandad's 119-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 105 between Javed Miandad and Mudassar Nazar
Javed Miandad has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (34) for PAK, going past Wasim Raja
